task.summary:
Big Updates!
- Animations are no longer tied to when components are repainted.
This caused a weird bug on pages with GWrappers. Animations would play faster since JComponents like to repaint themselves a lot.
- GTextBox now uses JTextFields instead of my custom code.
I was rather disappointed with my code since it was missing a lot of basic features and had some bugs with Windows. Now GTextBox uses a JTextField as a base and adds on features like the animated error messages. I still have the old boxes as GTextBoxOLD.
- Buttons now have rounded corners.
Mostly updating the features of GTextBox.
Starting to polish pages to their final version.
Added more TODO comments and gave an example of how things should be done.
added a few check, working on the logic now
